snippet.title: Frebbventure 0.4 - SAGE '21 teaser
snippet.description: The cat came back, they thought he was a goner, but the cat came back the very next SAGE! With shinier graphics, smoother gameplay, a funnier script than ever, and a solid serving of new content, Frebb's just about ready to give the world a second kick in the hiney!
